# NOTE: DO NOT IGNORE:
# - .mcp.json (MCP server configuration with env var references)
# - skills-lock.json (skill dependency lockfile, like package-lock.json)
# - .claude/settings.local.json (Claude Code project config)
# These should be committed as they're project configuration, not secrets

